------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Vendored components
------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The following modules are general-purpose libraries maintained alongside Tessera
and vendored into this repository so the server builds as a single, self-contained
project:

  * tessera-statemachine
    A pure-Java typed finite-state-machine library (no runtime dependencies).

  * tessera-observability
    Quarkus metrics/tracing defaults and a small readiness-probe framework.

Both were extracted from a shared internal commons library and relicensed under
the Apache License 2.0 for release with Tessera. If they later graduate to their
own published artifacts, this project will depend on them directly and these
vendored copies will be removed.
